DATA QUALITY ASSESSMENT REPORT

Dataset: Customer Data

1. Missing Values

* DOB column contained 1 missing value.

2. Duplicate Records

* 1 duplicate record was identified and removed.

3. Inconsistent Formatting

* City names appeared in different formats:

  * Hyderabad
  * HYDERABAD
  * hyderabad

* Standardized all city names to lowercase.

4. Date Format Issues

* RegistrationDate column contained multiple formats:

  * 01-05-2025
  * 2025/05/02
  * May 03 2025

* Converted all dates into a standard datetime format.

5. Feature Engineering

* Created a new column named Customer_Age from the DOB column.

6. Output

* Generated a cleaned and analysis-ready dataset named customer_cleaned.csv.
